plans.name: Starter support plan
plans.description: aiobs is seeking multiple open-source contributors to advance the project across multiple fronts, including adding support for additional LLM providers such as Anthropic, LLaMA, and vLLM, and expanding coverage of all API endpoints for OpenAI and Gemini. Future development plans also include integrating evaluation frameworks and prompt-enhancement utilities.
